casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Laing.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Laing (1993), 66 Ohio St.3d 1214.]

(No. 93-138 Submitted March 9, 1993 Decided March 10, 1993.)

The resignation of Robert Scott Laing as an attorney, Registration No. 0032529, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
